room_title: Escape room "Abandoned" by The SafeHouse in Tulsa
review: It was so much fun.  The clues are well planned out.  Excellent staff.  Out of all the escape rooms we've done, your #1.  Thanks!!!  Well worth the price too.

room_title: Escape room "Abandoned" by The SafeHouse in Tulsa
review: Lots of fun! Creepy mysteries, tantalizing stories and deliciously difficult puzzles to solve at times makes this escape the room experience well worthwhile.
